serialVersionUID: 3527286763882922740L

Serialized Fields

name

java.lang.String name
stores the name of the graph

id

int id
stores the ID of the graph

status

int[] status
stores the first deleted Edge/Node ([0/1]), the node/edge count([2/3]), and the max-node/edge index([4/5])

node_edges

int[][] node_edges
stores for each node in the array[nodeIndex] the degree ([x][0]), the in/outdegree ([x][1/2]) and the connected edge [x][3..]. It also contains the single linked deleted list at [x][NEXTEMPTY] in each deleted node. -1 marks the end of this list.

edge_nodes_and_direction

int[] edge_nodes_and_direction
stores the first node of each edge at [edgeIdx*3+NODEA], the second node at [edgeIdx*3+NODEB] and the direction in respect to nodeA at [edgeIdx*3+DIRECTION]. It also contains the single linked deleted list at [edgeIdx*3+NEXTEMPTY] in each deleted edge. -1 marks the end of the list.
